                    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The <code>paige/email</code> shortcode hides e-mail addresses from crawlers.</p>
<h2 id="address-parameter">Address parameter</h2>
<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-html-template" data-lang="go-html-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">email</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">address</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;example@example.com&#34;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">%</span><span class="cp">}}</span>E-mail me<span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">%</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">email</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">%</span><span class="cp">}}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>
<p><span class="paige-shortcode-email"><a href="" data-a="ZXhhbXBsZQ==" data-b="QA==" data-c="ZXhhbXBsZS5jb20=" onclick="this.href = 'mailto:' + atob(this.dataset.a) + atob(this.dataset.b) + atob(this.dataset.c)">E-mail me</a></span></p>]]></content>
                

